cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM 

This paper is primarily focused on image annotation, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The paper also discusses active learning, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) that deals with selecting the most informative samples for labeling. The use of metadata as a similarity metric and context for each image is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the experiments involve classification performance, which is a common evaluation metric in multimedia (cs.MM) research.
